metadata.name: Armin's All-Access #1
metadata.description: Armin’s All-Access is a Web3-based community for fans of Armin van Buuren. The digital art is created by Dutch designer Rik Oostenbroek and available in a total of ten eye-popping variations. In addition to the eight main color variations, there are also two special editions of exceeding rarity, each of which grants a special bonus perk on top of the AAA community access and perks. The token allows access to a gated channel in Armin’s Discord server and comes with a lot of utility. For more information, please visit:   Website: https://aaa.arminvanbuuren.com/ Discord: https://discord.com/invite/arminvanbuuren
